WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:03.600
The Barclays app

2
00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:06.200
How to change your personal details

3
00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.640
Changing your personal details couldn't
be easier with the Barclays app.

4
00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:14.760
Log in and from the home screen,
tap the profile icon.

5
00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:16.920
Choose what you need to update.

6
00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:20.600
To update your home address tap on ‘Home address’.

7
00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:25.480
Read the information about fraud and scams
and if you’re happy, tap ‘Next’.

8
00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:29.040
Enter your postcode and tap ‘Search’.

9
00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:32.680
Select your new address from the drop-down list.

10
00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:36.320
If you’re happy with the details, tap ‘Next’.

11
00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:39.840
Enter the date you moved into the property.

12
00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:43.720
Please note you should only change
your address once you have moved.

13
00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:49.680
Review the details and if you’re happy, tap ‘Confirm’.

14
00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:52.920
You’ve now updated your address for all your accounts.

15
00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:55.680
You can also update your employment information,

16
00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:58.520
email addresses and phone numbers

17
00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:05.120
and when prompted, tap ‘Save’.

18
00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:06.320
And that’s it,

19
00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:11.200
changing your personal details
made easy with the Barclays app.

